---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy – JEE Halt" canonical="/privacy-policy">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <Breadcrumb crumbs={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Privacy Policy' }]} />
    <div class="mt-6 card p-8 prose-section">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>JEE Halt does not require users to create accounts or provide personal information to access study material. We may collect anonymous usage data such as page views and browser type via analytics tools to improve our services.</p>

      <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use minimal cookies for site functionality such as remembering your dark/light mode preference. We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our website contains links to third-party download sources. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those external websites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before downloading any content.</p>

      <h2>4. Google Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. This service may collect anonymized data. You can opt out via Google's opt-out browser add-on.</p>

      <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our services are intended for students of all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected such information, please contact us immediately.</p>

      <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact" class="text-orange-400 hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-section :global(h1) { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #f8fafc; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose-section :global(h2) { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 1.75rem 0 0.6rem; }
  .prose-section :global(p) { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
</style>
